N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 3 ยง 203.32 - Daniel kelly

State Regulations

The Banking Board hereby grants permission for Daniel Kelly
to be at the same time a director of Hartford Trust Company and a limited
partner of Salomon Brothers, a New York Stock Exchange member firm and
underwriter. Notes
